      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2006 Mitsubishi Lancer Evolution IX MR in impeccable condition. This chassis features the highly sought-after 4G63 powerplant with MIVEC variable valve timing, delivering optimal volumetric efficiency and forced-induction response via its factory twin-scroll turbocharger. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed close-ratio manual gearbox and the sophisticated Active Center Differential (ACD), ensuring surgical handling characteristics. All mechanical components, including the Bilstein monotube dampers and Brembo four-piston calipers, remain in peak operational state. The vehicle retains all original VIN tags on factory body panels, showcasing an investment-grade exterior and an undercarriage free of oxidation. This is a turn-key example for the discerning purist, requiring zero deferred maintenance.",
